							\end{tikzpicture}
						</latex-image>
					</image>
				</figure>
			</sidebyside>
			Another way we can visualize <m>g(t)</m> is by imagining its graph, in <xref ref="intro-piecewise-function"/>, as the sum of the disconnected pieces in <xref ref="intro-piecewise-function-pieces"/>. 
